data.description: Don't miss this lovely 4 bd/3 bath split foyer house conveniently located to I-75, shopping, restaurants and less than a mile from the new Costco at the Bridges at Jodeco!  This home features new LVP flooring in living room, dining room and hallway, tile in kitchen and baths, kitchen includes all appliances and is open to the living room, master bedroom is on the main and includes trey ceiling, double vanity, garden tub, separate shower and walk-in closet, spacious 4th bedroom on lower level with full bathroom, 2 car garage with storage room and plenty of space in the level backyard for entertaining! A MUST SEE!!  **New a/c will be installed prior to closing**
